com.mozilla.secops.parser

Class Nginx

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mozilla.secops.parser.PayloadBase
      • com.mozilla.secops.parser.SourcePayloadBase
        • com.mozilla.secops.parser.Nginx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Nginx
extends SourcePayloadBase
implements Serializable
    Payload parser for nginx log data

    This parser currently only supports nginx log data that has been encapsulated in the jsonPayload section of a Stackdriver LogEntry.

    See Also:
